### 解题思路

此处撰写解题思路

### 代码

* python3

```python
class Solution:
    def isAnagram(self, s: str, t: str) -> bool:
        dic={}
        if len(s)!=len(t):
            return False
        for i in s:
            if dic.get(i):
                dic[i]+=1
            else:
                dic[i]=1
        for i in t:
            if dic.get(i):
                dic[i]-=1
            else:
                return False
        return True
```

